io.cloudex.framework.components

Class Coordinator

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.cloudex.framework.CommonExecutable
      • io.cloudex.framework.components.Coordinator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executable

    public class Coordinator
extends CommonExecutable
    The CloudEx Coordinator Component. Processor tasks can be run on VM configuration that is different from the ones used for the job. These VMs will be shutdown as soon as the task is completed and won't be added to the VM pool for reuse. This coordinator keeps track processor vms stats, such as start/end times, cost and vm config.
    Author:
    Omer Dawelbeit (omerio)
